The paper deals with generating natural questions from images, which involves using both visual and language modalities. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR). However, given that the paper focuses on generating questions from images, it is most likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category.
